      "description": "This 2014 Lincoln MKZ Hybrid is a sharp black sedan that delivers real efficiency without sacrificing the comfort you'd expect from Lincoln. With 158,675 miles on it, it's been well-used but it still runs strong. The black leather interior is in good shape, and you get a nice, quiet ride with the hybrid powertrain doing the work for you at the pump.\n\nThe MKZ feels more upscale than its price suggests. You're looking at a four-door sedan with a 2.0L 4-cylinder engine paired with hybrid technology, automatic transmission, and front-wheel drive. It's the kind of car that makes your commute feel a little easier.\n\nWe price our cars to move them, and at $7,999, this one won't sit long. If you want a reliable, efficient sedan with some style and a leather cabin, come take a look. You'll feel the difference when you sit down inside.",
